quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  55,26,Kullu men ÂṀaleyha famin
  55,27,Ve yebka vechu rabbike zulcelali velÂṀikrami
  55,28,Febieyyi alai rabbikuma tukezzibani
  55,29,YesÂṀeluhu men fiyssemavati velÂṀardÄḟ kulle yevmin huve fiy ÅeÂṀnin
  55,30,Febieyyi alai rabbikuma tukezzibani
  55,31,SenefruÄu lekum eyyuhessekaleni
  55,32,Febieyyi alai rabbikuma tukezzibani
  55,33,Ya maÂṀÅerelcinni velÂṀinsi inistetaÂṀtum en tenfusu min aktarissemavati velÂṀardÄḟ fenfuzu la tenfizune illa bisultanin
  55,34,Febieyyi alai rabbikuma tukezzibani
  55,35,Yurselu ÂṀaleykuma Åuvazun min narin ve nuhasun fela tentesÄḟrani
  55,36,Febieyyi alai rabbikuma tukezzibani
  55,37,FeizenÅakkatesissemau fekanet verdeten keddihani
  55,38,Febieyyi alai rabbikuma tukezzibani
  55,39,Feyevmeizin la yusÂṀelu ÂṀan zenbihi insun vela cannun
  55,40,Febieyyi alai rabbikuma tukezzibani
  55,41,YuÂṀrefulmucrimune bisiymahum feyuÂṀhazu binnevasÄḟy velÂṀakdami
  55,42,Febieyyi alai rabbikuma tukezzibani
  55,43,Hazihi cehennemulletiy yukezzibu bihelmucrimune
  55,44,Yetufune beyneha ve beyne hamiymin anin
